    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374660/extras/b1f15560c4be3b1efa48063f0bf64d7d.avif?t=1758797020\" width=616 height=348 /></span><br>这是一款第三人称射击加轻度解密游戏,主要剧情是在未来某处进行着一项秘密实验<br>在此过程中发现了一种奇特的矿石,并引发了大规模感染<br>局势失控,所有未感染者全部撤离<br>而主角的任务是必须取回重要的&quot;档案&quot;并逃离这个地方!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374660/extras/d42fd7a4bfb89b7c8dd5dac205e43b72.poster.avif?t=1758797020\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374660/extras/d42fd7a4bfb89b7c8dd5dac205e43b72.webm?t=1758797020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374660/extras/d42fd7a4bfb89b7c8dd5dac205e43b72.mp4?t=1758797020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏共有三把武器,分别为手枪,步枪以及霰弹枪<br>同时拥有两种辅助武器,分别为防身匕首和手雷<br>游戏中还存在合成弹药系统,玩家可根据喜好合成自己想要的弹药<br><br><br>游戏特色与玩法<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374660/extras/b27f4d312c2b2a09a8b6993aa311cef5.poster.avif?t=1758797020\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374660/extras/b27f4d312c2b2a09a8b6993aa311cef5.webm?t=1758797020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374660/extras/b27f4d312c2b2a09a8b6993aa311cef5.mp4?t=1758797020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏采用箱庭式地图,玩家需要探索区域,找寻线索解开谜题,击败敌人逃离这个地方!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374660/extras/9589bdcee5d285e6325a687619d029a5.webp?t=1758797020\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374660/extras/9589bdcee5d285e6325a687619d029a5.poster.avif?t=1758797020\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=348 /></picture></span><br>同时在地图中散落着各种不同款式的衣服,一经解锁便可前往拍照模式进行游玩!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374660/extras/b5ab9f5d47a3d0c28fae7a55b2a13c2c.avif?t=1758797020\" width=616 height=348 /></span><br>游戏新增自定义身材选项,不管您是喜欢丰满的还是苗条的都可以在这里找到!",
